{"tid":2310944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違反限聚令罰一萬蚊，是嚴刑峻法，不是防疫，是打劫。","createTime":"2020-12-03T15:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T23:36:20.000Z","uid":261647,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c06669f02c993b8ce05d249c234a85397b0d422","tid":2310944,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chengchungtai/posts/1693095454198138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchengchungtai%2Fposts%2F1693095454198138&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=08df19c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chengchungtai/posts/1693095454198138</a><br />\n<br />\n違反限聚令罰一萬蚊，是嚴刑峻法，不是防疫，是打劫。<br />\n<br />\n過去大半年，我相信大部分人同意，本港社會對抗所謂的「瘟疫」，全賴市民的自律，以及人民之間的互諒互讓。<br />\n<br />\n然而，政府沒有檢討自己抗疫不力，尤其是豁免強制檢驗的措施。每每發生本地爆發，便借機收緊市民的日常生活空間，甚至強推健康碼等電子監控經濟系統入侵私人生活。<br />\n<br />\n加上執法部門向來選擇撿控，一貫欺壓百姓。<br />\n<br />\n瘟疫政治，就是極權以人民「健康」之名，行（電子）暴政之實。"},{"pid":"ba52a2f533ff9e0586fa2d4070aa65c3f238e106","tid":2310944,"uid":228955,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"根本就詐詐諦諦唔封關講乜都冇用"},{"pid":"1f6908f7bf36d5f7e112392212bc29788cc23ff4","tid":2310944,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"根本就係政治打壓啦. <br />\n你睇下公園D 藍絲廢佬? 黑警行過扮睇唔到. <br />\n之前經過油麻地香港仔魚蛋王, 過咗堂食時間擺晒枱擺晒椅出嚟, 見住2隻黑警喺道買外賣."},{"pid":"cb64bb19980ca1c3821372a92da38910b5745772","tid":2310944,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"熱狗又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d755f91f77c5fdcbdbdf969572a4bedbb8e3fe","tid":2310944,"uid":292544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"係出比網台記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個出去都要食599<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ceb685c443c07bb9afb39ab3d14759a73e2ec4","tid":2310944,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"如果係一視同仁我唔介意<br />\n<br />\n但現實就係藍屍廢老唔捉<br />\n<br />\n黑底餐廳(火鍋店果類)晚晚一班人食飯扮睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n元朗果間嘉麗園之前晚晚過12點照做生意咪又係乜事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5557a8ec6ebd3baf9dc0d9d5eb3cfcc8b04ceebf","tid":2310944,"uid":374427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位黎...<br />\n<br />\n想請大家入黎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年嘅平安夜有咩做?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2310983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2310983</a>"},{"pid":"b8f9df605bd46454e677e5d40df74672f77d72bf","tid":2310944,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T23:36:20.000Z","msg":"自己友就唔洗同佢搏<br />\n借刀殺藍group 就 ok"}]}